<text top="1566" left="32" width="545" height="50" font="font13" id="p1_t44" reading_order_no="46" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">bastard,  had  affairs  with  her  broth- </text>
<text top="1610" left="32" width="544" height="50" font="font13" id="p1_t45" reading_order_no="47" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">ers-In-law  and  even  seduced  a </text>
<text top="1654" left="32" width="266" height="49" font="font14" id="p1_t46" reading_order_no="48" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">Puritan  preacher. </text>
<text top="1696" left="83" width="493" height="51" font="font12" id="p1_t47" reading_order_no="49" segment_no="9" tag_type="text">In  her  daring  new  biography, </text>
